org.eclipse.ui.views.properties.tabbed

Interface IOverridableTabList

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractOverridableTabListPropertySection

    public interface IOverridableTabList
    Represents a list of tabs. Used by a section that overrides the tabs that are provided by the tabbed property registry with a new list of tabs.

    The overridable tab list is a content provider that provides both the sections and the tab labels.

    Since:
    3.4
